'''Jana Stojanovska''' (born [[February 19]], [[1985]] in [[Skopje]], [[Republic of Macedonia]]) is a model who will represent her country in the [[57th Miss World pageant]], which will take place September 2007.
Jana, who stands 5' 7" (171cm) tall, competed in the national beauty pageant Miss Macedonia, held in [[Skopje]], [[Republic of Macedonia]] on [[September 5]], [[2007]] and obtained the title of Miss Macedonia for Miss World.
